Regulation (EC) No 889/2008 is amended as follows:
(1) in Article 63(1), the following point (d) is added:
‘(d) the specific characteristics of the production method used, where the operator intends to request documentary evidence in accordance with Article 68(2).’;
(2) Article 68 is replaced by the following:
(3) in the title of Annex XII, the reference to ‘Article 68’ is replaced by a reference to ‘Article 68(1)’;
(4) Annexes XIIa and XIIb are inserted as set out in Annex I to this Regulation.
